{"tid":1844491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府宣佈聽朝九點隔離1113個湖北旅客！！！","createTime":"2020-01-26T15:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:59:49.000Z","uid":1249,"like":30,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b6486f3b643c30a85442a95310e7ae481f4bad31","tid":1844491,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"不過係澳門政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175c7960908fab63145584afd15823693954c92c","tid":1844491,"uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"因應新型冠狀病毒疫情最新情況，政府發新聞稿指出，將於明（27）日上午9時起，把2019年12月1日至2020年1月26日入境澳門且不離開的1,113名湖北省旅客進行集中統一管理，在隔離中心隔離至簽註有效期滿 / 計劃行程期末送離澳門，如有旅客隔離中心發病，將即時送走進行隔離及醫治。<br />\n而政府亦指，在澳門的湖北省人士，如調查後發現無病徵，可選擇自行返回內地；如湖北旅客堅持留澳，則以上述隔離中心方法處理。湖北省外地僱員及學生則不在此列。<br />\n而社會文化司司長歐陽瑜指出，現時在澳門的湖北人共有2,132人，其中1,113多人為旅客，24人為在澳讀書學生，9,78人為外地僱員。而相關隔離中心，將會設在黑沙青年中心及市政署黑沙海灘培訓中心。（編輯：陳嘉俊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/139632.html?channel=wechat&amp;from=groupmessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F139632.html%3Fchannel%3Dwechat%26from%3Dgroupmessage%26isappinstalled%3D0&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=c90d5377\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/139632.html?channel=wechat&amp;from=groupmessage&amp;isappinstalled=0</a>"},{"pid":"b77afc55b3eef6c76a98479bd4e53484334fba54","tid":1844491,"uid":307203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:50:45.000Z","msg":"澳共&gt;港共<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武漢x香港】手足聯動，五大訴求，延燒大陸！ 就蔥友和香港手足聯合發起文宣戰倡議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bcbbe5c647b7508a15109df9e632b5adc9682d71","tid":1844491,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2